{"id":300818,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-上海市民第103次向人大请愿要求诉权，人大/","date":"2013-06-26T00:03:03Z","modified":"2013-06-26T00:03:03Z","title":"维权网 | 上海市民第103次向人大请愿要求诉权，人大闭门无人接待（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>日 星期一下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>时，维护公民诉权的<span lang=\"EN-US\">79</span>名上海市民代表，为了捍卫法律尊严，为了上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">1060</span>户被剥夺诉权的家庭，第<span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span>次集体向市人大请愿，要求人大监督法院维护公民诉权、清除司法不作为。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>多年来上海大量的掠夺农民土地案、强拆房屋案、迫害拘留案、劳教案、非法拘禁案等“民告官”的案子，上海各法院既不立案也不裁定，市民代表已经<span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span>次要求市人大履行职责。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今天大家推荐赵迪迪、郑培培、黄尧年、周荣清、陈伟华等<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>名市民为代表。下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分，<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>名代表走到<span lang=\"EN-US\">105</span>接待室（以往是 费 老师在该接待室里接待市民代表），看见接待室门紧锁。保安说：“门口的灯也不亮，没人接待”。当<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>名代表要求保安安排到其他接待室接待时，保安说：“你们自己看门口的灯”。大家一看，其他接待室门口的灯也不亮，说明没有人接待。大家百思不得其解，星期一下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分属于上班时间，人大接待员怎么不上班呢？你们拿了纳税人的钱，在做些什么？预先没有人收到星期一不接待的通知书，到了星期一为什么人大接待员躲藏起来不接待市民？ <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>随后，<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>名代表和等候在大厅里的市民代表一起走出人大信访办门口，迎面停着一辆车牌号“沪·<span lang=\"EN-US\">E8659</span>警”的警车里出来<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>名警察，阻止代表们拍集体照。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家只好又到人民公园门口拍了一张《上海市民代表第<span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span>次集体向市人大请愿、我要立案、捍卫法律、还我诉权》的集体照。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与第<span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span>次“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动的<span lang=\"EN-US\">79</span>名市民代表强烈要求市人大履行法定职责，维护法律尊严，保障公民诉权。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动请与下述市民代表联系：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>焦东海（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13801802454</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>鲁<span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span>俊（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13651817422</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>赵迪迪（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13482668387</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13042111402</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155</span>）【为十八大维稳被逮捕】<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>童国菁（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13917920278</span>）【为十八大维稳被劳教】<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13564097383</span>）【为十八大维稳被劳教】<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉华（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13162424968</span>） <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15001903401</span>） <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>刘洪贤（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13524850369</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>郑培培（<span lang=\"EN-US\">02153963826</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>孙建敏（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13671947476</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15026516445</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-s20tDILru0M/Ucm1jbDoAVI/AAAAAAAAkLs/ef7r4szvpD4/s1600/8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"192\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-s20tDILru0M/Ucm1jbDo